Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakuta memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.53,0:23:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamu memang bajingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:24:00.01,5-normal,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,408)\fs68\b1\bord0}Selanjutnya
